results.definition: humble in spirit or manner; suggesting retiring mildness or even cowed submissiveness

examples: meek as a mouse"- Langston Hughes

results.definition: evidencing little spirit or courage; overly submissive or compliant
examples: compliant and anxious to suit his opinions of those of others
a fine fiery blast against meek conformity"- Orville Prescott
she looked meek but had the heart of a lion
